        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stop Judge Shopping Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill grants original and exclusive jurisdiction to the U.S. District Court for the District of Columbia over any civil action for declaratory or injunctive relief against the enforcement of a federal law if the relief extends beyond the parties involved.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
